{"pid":"6d55d5c0095fc54c8eb7a44a2a5c4ddb7b69d0cd","tid":960301,"uid":76276,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T11:15:43.000Z","msg":"第一季真係睇到r撚哂頭，次次睇完多一篇有d眉目果陣下篇又爆d新迷團出黎話你知你既推理唔合理。<br />\n但套野真係好好睇 op好入味，細個16,7歲果陣睇完都淆到唔敢出房。"},{"pid":"5f176cb6ff724f24d08589340dd593985c66e03f","tid":960301,"uid":191926,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T11:15:50.000Z","msg":"咪啪<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e42e0074bc4fe438aaed80eb833385116540196b","tid":960301,"uid":13151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T11:21:42.000Z","msg":"寒蟬真心好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4758896dc3dbb59a32cb69b0759cb255fc7b5138","tid":960301,"uid":171310,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T11:27:53.000Z","msg":"相對之下海貓真係好垃圾"},{"pid":"562b6f6cb17b6c874169c6ba71debea41a1b5dfc","tid":960301,"uid":69661,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T11:29:56.000Z","msg":"以前睇第一季嚇到賴屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"533aafe28f8c9d57079f20463ece0a3d4f268b85","tid":960301,"uid":11911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"29bdae127a057669aa02d18f7c1e515a8c2e832f","tid":960301,"uid":67896,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T11:05:24.000Z","msg":"海貓好睇啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T11:30:49.000Z","msg":"海貓睇過動畫麻麻地喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啲人話要玩game定睇漫畫先好"},{"pid":"7246056115560862aa7115863aa9f6a8f1bc3157","tid":960301,"uid":67896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"533aafe28f8c9d57079f20463ece0a3d4f268b85","tid":960301,"uid":11911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"29bdae127a057669aa02d18f7c1e515a8c2e832f","tid":960301,"uid":67896,